and possibly killed someone. We need to go.

322
00:21:05,282 --> 00:21:07,117
他可能會受傷 崔博士？
He could be hurt. Dr. Choi?

323
00:21:07,184 --> 00:21:08,985
急救人員正在趕來
First responders are on their way,

324
00:21:09,052 --> 00:21:11,155
但他們有問題，因為這是一個挖掘現場
but they've got questions because it's a dig site.

325
00:21:12,423 --> 00:21:14,057
哈囉? Hello?

326
00:21:15,125 --> 00:21:16,360
帕特裡克，我們走
Patrick, let's go.

327
00:21:18,796 --> 00:21:20,798
帕特裡克! Patrick!

328
00:21:20,863 --> 00:21:22,232
帕特裡克...Patrick...

329
00:21:22,299 --> 00:21:23,966


330
00:21:31,275 --> 00:21:33,177


331
00:21:33,243 --> 00:21:34,745
帕特裡克! Patrick!

332
00:21:34,812 --> 00:21:35,945
帕特裡克! 阿德裡安
Patrick! Adrian.

333
00:21:36,012 --> 00:21:37,247
帕特裡克，我們走
Patrick, let's go.

334
00:21:37,314 --> 00:21:39,015
等等，那是薩吉亞斯博士
Wait, wait, that's Dr. Sagias.

335
00:21:40,617 --> 00:21:41,552
哦，我的天啊!
Oh my God.

336
00:21:41,618 --> 00:21:42,885
尼克? Nick?

337
00:21:42,952 --> 00:21:45,422
別碰我 Don't touch me.

338
00:21:45,489 --> 00:21:47,491
沒事的，薩吉亞斯博士
It's okay, Dr. Sagias.

339
00:21:47,558 --> 00:21:48,958
你在挖掘現場
You're at the dig site.

340
00:21:49,025 --> 00:21:50,728
那發生了爆炸
There was an explosion.

341
00:21:50,794 --> 00:21:53,831
尼克，是我，阿德裡安·奎因
Nick, it's me, Adrian Quinn.

342
00:21:53,896 --> 00:21:55,132
你...你受傷了嗎？你沒事吧？
Are you...Are you hurt? Are you okay?

343
00:21:55,199 --> 00:21:56,966
我不需要你的幫助，好嗎？
I don't want your help, okay?

344
00:21:59,570 --> 00:22:01,171
他們找到他了
They found him.

345
00:22:01,238 --> 00:22:03,940
是的，他衹是有點震驚
Yeah, he's just a little stunned.

346
00:22:04,006 --> 00:22:05,275
好了，各位，這裡不安全
All right, everybody, it's not safe here.

347
00:22:05,342 --> 00:22:06,810
我們必須把所有人都救出來
We got to get everybody out.

348
00:22:06,876 --> 00:22:08,345
先生? 薩吉亞斯博士
Sir? Dr. Sagias,

349
00:22:08,412 --> 00:22:10,714
我帶你到地面，好嗎？
I'm going to lead you to the surface, all right?

350
00:22:10,781 --> 00:22:13,250
離我遠點 你們所有的人！
Stay away from me. All of you!

351
00:22:13,317 --> 00:22:17,087
尼克 是我，格雷斯
Nick. It's me, Grace.

352
00:22:18,756 --> 00:22:23,527
我現在不需要你的幫助
I do not require your assistance at this time.

353
00:22:23,594 --> 00:22:25,462
你為什麼在這裡，尼克？
Why are you here, Nick?

354
00:22:26,963 --> 00:22:28,898
我來...I came...

355
00:22:28,965 --> 00:22:31,235
親自來訪問芬利爾監獄
to visit the prison of Fenrir myself.

356
00:22:33,470 --> 00:22:35,539
你怎麼知道這是芬利爾的監獄？
How did you know this was the prison of Fenrir?

357
00:22:37,074 --> 00:22:38,275
我們需要出去外面
We need to go outside.

358
00:22:38,342 --> 00:22:40,344
這個房間太不穩定了
This room is too unstable.

359
00:22:40,411 --> 00:22:41,978
我們需要離開
We need to leave.

360
00:22:42,044 --> 00:22:45,649
那很好 我和帕特裡克一起去
That's fine. I'll go with Patrick here.

361
00:22:45,716 --> 00:22:48,352
你們都離開
You all leave.

362
00:22:49,820 --> 00:22:51,422
好的 Okay.

363
00:22:51,488 --> 00:22:55,459
你找到他了？我很好，很好，衹是-是的
You got him? I'm fine, fine, just-yeah.

364
00:23:08,572 --> 00:23:10,541
呃-呃 Uh-uh.

365
00:23:12,342 --> 00:23:13,911
你覺得尼克看起來不太對勁了嗎？
Did Nick seem off to you?

366
00:23:13,976 --> 00:23:16,847
有人說他會出現在現場上
No one said anything about him showing up to the site.

367
00:23:16,914 --> 00:23:18,148
他就是這樣
He's like that.

368
00:23:18,215 --> 00:23:20,016
