00:23:24,087 --> 00:23:26,055
對 Right.

372
00:23:26,123 --> 00:23:28,192
看，尼克很古怪
Look, Nick is eccentric.

373
00:23:29,326 --> 00:23:31,495
可能被爆炸震暈了
Could have been stunned from the blast.

374
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:36,400
你注意到他沒有跛行嗎？他總是拿著枴杖
Did you notice he's not limping? He always has a cane.

375
00:23:36,467 --> 00:23:39,001
我的意思是，我們應該聽他說，或者至少看到他
I mean, we should have heard him or at least seen him.

376
00:23:39,069 --> 00:23:40,904
他是怎麼從我們身邊溜過去的？
How'd he sneak past us?

377
00:23:40,970 --> 00:23:43,474
我要打幾通電話 我不知道發生了什麼
I'm gonna make a few calls. I'm not sure what's going on,

378
00:23:43,540 --> 00:23:46,543
但這感覺不對 我要回去
but it doesn't feel right. I'm going to go back.

379
00:23:46,610 --> 00:23:48,445
什麼? What?

380
00:23:50,314 --> 00:23:52,749
我衹是想知道你是否值得拯救
I was just wondering if you were worth saving.

381
00:23:52,816 --> 00:23:54,485
你說什麼? Excuse me?

382
00:23:54,551 --> 00:23:58,054
我以為你想讓我幫你離開這裡，薩吉亞斯博士
I thought you wanted me to help you out of here, Dr. Sagias.

383
00:23:59,656 --> 00:24:00,824
那就幫忙吧!
Then help.

384
00:24:00,891 --> 00:24:03,660


385
00:24:03,727 --> 00:24:04,994
這是安全部門，我是葛列格
You reached security, this is Greg.

386
00:24:05,061 --> 00:24:05,995
我能幫你什麼？
How can I help you?

387
00:24:06,062 --> 00:24:07,531
是的 嗨，我是格雷斯.崔
Yes. Hi, I'm Grace Choi.

388
00:24:07,598 --> 00:24:09,166
我是與薩吉亞斯合作的考古學家之一
I'm one of the archeologists working with Sagias.

389
00:24:09,233 --> 00:24:10,701
我想知道我是否可以和他談談
I was wondering if I could speak with him.

390
00:24:10,767 --> 00:24:13,704
恐怕薩吉亞斯博士正在開會
I'm afraid that Dr. Sagias is in a meeting.

391
00:24:13,770 --> 00:24:14,972
你得晚點再打來
You have to call back later.

392
00:24:15,037 --> 00:24:16,507
他正在開會？
He's in a meeting?

393
00:24:17,875 --> 00:24:19,409
他去現場了嗎？
Did he go to the site?

394
00:24:19,476 --> 00:24:23,012
沒有，我大約10分鐘前剛到他家吃午飯
No, I just buzzed in his lunch about 10 minutes ago.

395
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:25,482
他一整天待在博物館了
He's been at the museum all day.

396
00:24:25,549 --> 00:24:28,519
好的 謝謝 當然
Okay. Thanks. Of course.

397
00:24:28,585 --> 00:24:30,687
還有什麼我能幫忙的嗎？
Is there anything else I can help with?

398
00:24:30,754 --> 00:24:32,689
有什麼問題嗎？
Is there anything wrong?

399
00:24:32,756 --> 00:24:34,625
你能讓他開會完後打電話給我嗎？
Could you have him call me when he's done?

400
00:24:34,691 --> 00:24:36,226
告訴他這很重要
Tell him it's important.

401
00:24:36,293 --> 00:24:38,595
當然 我會讓他馬上給你回電話
Certainly. I'll have him call you back at once.

402
00:24:38,662 --> 00:24:40,097
謝謝，葛列格
Thanks, Greg.

403
00:24:43,734 --> 00:24:44,801
哈樂德 是的?
Harold. Yeah?

404
00:24:44,868 --> 00:24:46,103
把你的無線電扔給我
Toss me your radio.

405
00:24:48,272 --> 00:24:50,240


406
00:24:50,307 --> 00:24:53,577
帕特裡克？奎因？
Patrick? Quinn?

407
00:24:53,644 --> 00:24:55,546
聽到嗎，完畢？
Come in, over?

408
00:24:58,882 --> 00:25:00,817
有人能聽到我說話嗎，完畢？
Can anyone hear me, over?

409
00:25:03,420 --> 00:25:06,523
來吧，跟我來
Come on. Follow me.

410
00:25:17,768 --> 00:25:20,370


411
00:25:23,073 --> 00:25:25,776
這都是什麼？
What is all this?

412
00:25:25,842 --> 00:25:28,312
一個哨所站
A sentry station.

413
00:25:31,848 --> 00:25:35,252
警衛？為了什麼？
Guards? For what?

414
00:25:41,158 --> 00:25:43,226
芬利爾 Fenrir.

415
00:25:45,963 --> 00:25:47,164
尼克! Nick!

416
00:25:47,230 --> 00:25:50,167
尼克，住手！終於
Nick, stop! At last.

417
00:25:50,233 --> 00:25:51,802
住手 Stop.

418
00:25:51,868 --> 00:25:55,073
對不起，像這樣的事情是有程序的
I'm sorry, but there are procedures for stuff like this.

419
00:25:55,138 --> 00:25:56,573
我很抱歉？I'm sorry?

420
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:58,709
你不能只從挖掘現場拿走東西
You can't just take things from an excavation site.

421
00:25:58,775 --> 00:26:00,344
我們必須記錄下來
We have to log it.

422
00:26:00,410 --> 00:26:02,713
但更重要的是，我們現在必須離開這裡
But more importantly, we have to get out of here now.

423
00:26:02,779 --> 00:26:05,115
薩吉亞斯博士...
Dr. Sagias...

424
00:26:05,182 --> 00:26:08,051
打開骨灰盒
Open the urn.

425
00:26:08,151 --> 00:26:11,121
尼克! 現在 打開骨灰盒
Nick! Now. Open the urn.

426
00:26:16,493 --> 00:26:18,862
帕特裡克 帕特裡克，住手！
Patrick. Patrick, stop!

427
00:26:34,911 --> 00:26:37,347
我不能呼吸
I can't breathe.

428
00:26:46,857 --> 00:26:48,725


429
00:26:59,103 --> 00:27:01,371
好多了 謝謝你，博士
Much better. Thank you, Doctor.

430
00:27:01,438 --> 00:27:03,573
沒有你的幫助，我永遠無法
Without your assistance, I would've never

431
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:07,411
找回大灰狼的毒牙
been able to retrieve the Great Wolf's fang.

432
00:27:09,579 --> 00:27:12,116
你不能移動它
You can't remove that.

433
00:27:12,182 --> 00:27:13,917
我不明白 I don't understand.

434
00:27:13,984 --> 00:27:15,519
你是誰？Who are you?

435
00:27:15,585 --> 00:27:18,622
我的禮貌在哪裡？
Where are my manners?

436
00:27:18,689 --> 00:27:20,757
為什麼，我是洛基
Why, I'm Loki.

437
00:27:22,793 --> 00:27:25,328
離他遠一點
Get away from him.

438
00:27:25,395 --> 00:27:27,197
那不是尼克
That's not Nick.

439
00:27:27,264 --> 00:27:28,532
就是那個傢伙！
That's the guy!

440
00:27:28,598 --> 00:27:29,933
就是那個通過我的傢伙
That's the guy that got past me.

441
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,435
你想要什麼？
What do you want?

442
00:27:33,171 --> 00:27:35,106
當然，這理所應當地是我的
What's rightfully mine, of course.

443
00:27:35,173 --> 00:27:37,108
他在某種程度上控制著帕特裡克
He's controlling Patrick somehow.

444
00:27:37,175 --> 00:27:38,208
格雷斯，我們必須離開這裡
Grace, we got to get out of here.

445
00:27:38,275 --> 00:27:39,943
你對帕特裡克做了什麼？
What have you done to Patrick?

446
00:27:43,914 --> 00:27:45,649
很不幸，奧丁成功了
Well, unfortunately, Odin made it

447
00:27:45,716 --> 00:27:50,387
所以，上帝無法挖掘出這隻大灰狼
so that a God is unable to unearth the Great Wolf.

448
00:27:51,421 --> 00:27:54,725
所以我需要一個凡人
So I needed a mortal,

449
00:27:56,059 --> 00:27:59,163
而這裡的好博士很樂意也很能幹
and the good doctor here was willing and able.

450
00:27:59,229 --> 00:28:01,498
而現在我有了毒牙...
And now that I have the fang...

451
00:28:03,266 --> 00:28:07,270
還有一件事要做
there's just one more thing to do.

452
00:28:07,337 --> 00:28:08,939


453
00:28:09,005 --> 00:28:11,041
帕特裡克! Patrick!

454
00:28:11,109 --> 00:28:14,478
不! 離開這裡！走! 
No! Get out of here! Go!

455
00:28:14,544 --> 00:28:18,381
救你自己！走! 啊！
Save yourself! Go! Ah!

456
00:28:18,448 --> 00:28:20,450
你聽到他了，救你自己
You heard him, save yourself.

457
00:28:20,517 --> 00:28:23,420
走! 救你自己！走! 
Go! Save yourselves! Go!

458
00:28:25,722 --> 00:28:28,024


459
00:28:39,137 --> 00:28:41,271
啊！Ah!

460
00:28:42,339 --> 00:28:43,974
你沒事吧？是的，我想是的
Are you okay? Yeah, I think so.

461
00:28:52,183 --> 00:28:55,318
他在那裡 There he is.

462
00:29:01,525 --> 00:29:03,927
我想知道你什麼時候會出現，索爾
I was wondering when you'd show up, Thor.

463
00:29:03,994 --> 00:29:05,529
看起來你沒有想像中那麼善於
Looks like you were not as good

464
00:29:05,595 --> 00:29:07,697
隱藏自己的行蹤
at hiding your whereabouts as you think.

465
00:29:07,764 --> 00:29:10,300
你將為你對阿斯加德的罪行付出代價
You will pay for your crimes against Asgard.

466
00:29:10,367 --> 00:29:13,436
罪行？什麼罪行？

467
00:29:13,503 --> 00:29:16,740
解放這個星球？解放凡人
Liberating this planet? Freeing the mortals.

468
00:29:16,807 --> 00:29:19,342
我相信是你犯的罪行，索爾
I believe you're the one committing the crime, Thor.

469
00:29:20,710 --> 00:29:21,945


470
00:29:23,914 --> 00:29:24,948


471
00:29:42,833 --> 00:29:47,205
恐怕太晚了，因為芬利爾甦醒了
I'm afraid it's too late, for Fenrir is awake.

472
00:29:47,271 --> 00:29:49,573


473
00:29:59,250 --> 00:30:01,384


474
00:30:03,321 --> 00:30:05,289
世界末日即將到來
The end of the world is near.

475
00:30:05,355 --> 00:30:07,158
我必須跑走了
I must run.

476
00:30:07,225 --> 00:30:09,526
不 不! 洛基！
No. No! Loki!

477
00:30:12,729 --> 00:30:14,764
洛基！Loki!

478
00:30:16,433 --> 00:30:17,834


479
00:30:17,901 --> 00:30:20,704
你還好嗎？是的，我想是的
You okay? Yeah, I think so.

480
00:30:25,343 --> 00:30:27,278
等等，格雷斯！
Wait, Grace!

481
00:30:27,345 --> 00:30:29,113
等等，等等 Wait, wait.

482
00:30:42,492 --> 00:30:43,927
對不起 Excuse me.

483
00:30:45,028 --> 00:30:46,696
嗨，呃...Hi, uh...

484
00:30:49,133 --> 00:30:51,269
我是，呃...格雷斯
I'm, uh...Grace.

485
00:30:51,335 --> 00:30:53,304
我是格雷斯.崔博士
I'm Dr. Grace Choi.

486
00:30:53,371 --> 00:30:56,506
我是這次挖掘的現場經理
I'm site manager at this excavation.

487
00:30:56,573 --> 00:30:59,243
嗯，呃-呃 Um, uh-uh.

488
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:02,179
那是洛基，所以...
That's Loki, so...

489
00:31:03,413 --> 00:31:06,016
你一定是索爾
You must be Thor.

490
00:31:06,083 --> 00:31:07,984
你知道我的名字？
You know of my name?

491
00:31:09,519 --> 00:31:11,355
怎麼知道? How?

492
00:31:11,421 --> 00:31:14,658
噢...錘子
Well...the hammer.

493
00:31:15,792 --> 00:31:17,527
雷神之錘？Mjolnir?

494
00:31:17,594 --> 00:31:19,562
你知道他嗎？
You know of it?

495
00:31:19,629 --> 00:31:21,932
北歐神話是我的專長
Norse mythology is my specialty.

496
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:25,435
噢...Well...

497
00:31:25,502 --> 00:31:27,171
我猜，不是神話
Not mythology, I guess.

498
00:31:29,005 --> 00:31:30,874
你研究了我們
You studied us.

499
00:31:30,941 --> 00:31:32,909
那麼你可能知道洛基在哪裡
Then you may know where Loki is.

500
00:31:32,976 --> 00:31:34,245
你可以幫我
You can help me.

501
00:31:34,312 --> 00:31:36,880
嗯，也許？Um, maybe?

502
00:31:38,682 --> 00:31:41,718
你的世界的命運取決於它
The fate of your world depends upon it

503
00:31:41,785 --> 00:31:43,887
還有你對我們的了解
and your knowledge of us.

504
00:31:44,754 --> 00:31:47,158
噢，當你這樣說的時候
Well, when you put it like that.

505
00:31:50,227 --> 00:31:51,461
跟我來 Come with me.

506
00:31:53,463 --> 00:31:54,965
好的 Okay.

507
00:32:07,078 --> 00:32:09,679
芬利爾的毒牙 不要碰那個
The Fang of Fenrir. Do not touch that.

508
00:32:09,746 --> 00:32:12,582
等等，你臉上的斑紋怎麼了？
Wait, what happened to the markings on your face?

509
00:32:12,649 --> 00:32:14,684
神的戰爭畫作
War paint of the gods.

510
00:32:14,751 --> 00:32:16,820
它在戰鬥中顯示出來
It manifests during battle.

511
00:32:21,459 --> 00:32:23,526
等等-嘿！Wait-hey!

512
00:32:42,279 --> 00:32:45,648
那是伊格德拉西爾，九界之樹
That's Yggdrasil, the tree of the Nine Realms.

513
00:32:45,715 --> 00:32:46,916
你知道它？
You know of it?

514
00:32:46,983 --> 00:32:48,319
是的 Yeah.

515
00:32:48,386 --> 00:32:51,255
基本上每個分支都包含宇宙的一部分
Basically each branch holds a part of the universe.

516
00:32:51,322 --> 00:32:52,490
地球是它的一部分
Earth is part of it.

517
00:32:52,555 --> 00:32:55,493
這就是洛基追求的
This is what Loki is after.

518
00:32:55,558 --> 00:32:57,328
他尋找來摧毀這棵樹
He seeks to destroy the tree

519
00:32:57,395 --> 00:33:00,730
而種植一種他可以控制的新品種
and plant a new one that he could control.

520
00:33:00,797 --> 00:33:02,932
而這就是為什麼他需要芬利爾？
And that's why he needs Fenrir?

521
00:33:02,999 --> 00:33:05,869
洛基可以摧毀這棵樹
Loki can destroy the tree.

522
00:33:07,238 --> 00:33:10,141
但是攻擊每一個領域，這將是困難的
But attacking each realm, that will be difficult.

523
00:33:10,207 --> 00:33:13,477
芬利爾會變得越來越強大
Fenrir will grow stronger and bigger,

524
00:33:13,543 --> 00:33:15,413
而它將吞噬每一個領域
and he will devour each realm.

525
00:33:15,479 --> 00:33:17,881
樹在哪裡？
Where's the tree?

526
00:33:17,947 --> 00:33:20,317
我父親說它在附近
My father said it's nearby.

527
00:33:20,384 --> 00:33:24,221
當芬利爾離它太近時，他被監禁了
Fenrir was imprisoned when he got too close to it.

528
00:33:24,288 --> 00:33:28,658
眾神阻止了芬利爾 我們衹是凡人
The gods stopped Fenrir. We are just mortals.

529
00:33:28,725 --> 00:33:31,462
沒有人要求你這麼做
No one is asking you to do this.

530
00:33:31,529 --> 00:33:33,297
我將親自接受這個挑戰
I will take on this challenge myself.

531
00:33:33,364 --> 00:33:35,132
不，我們不能讓帕特裡剋死
No, we can't let Patrick die.

532
00:33:35,199 --> 00:33:36,699
你的朋友是對的
Your friend is right.

533
00:33:36,766 --> 00:33:38,902
芬利爾變得更加強大
Fenrir grows more powerful

534
00:33:38,968 --> 00:33:40,670
而你的朋友，他將永遠消失
and your friend, he will disappear forever.

535
00:33:40,737 --> 00:33:42,073
我們可以阻止他們
We can stop them.

536
00:33:44,508 --> 00:33:46,444
這就是我喜歡你們這種人的地方
This is what I like about your kind.

537
00:33:46,510 --> 00:33:47,777
機會對你不利
The odds are against you.

538
00:33:47,844 --> 00:33:49,779
然而你們卻選擇了為彼此而戰
Yet you choose to fight for one another.

539
00:33:49,846 --> 00:33:53,117
我們能和他們戰鬥嗎？不
Can we fight them? No.

540
00:33:53,184 --> 00:33:56,387
衹要告訴我他們在哪裡，我會自己和他們戰鬥
Just tell me where they are and I will fight them on my own.

541
00:33:56,454 --> 00:34:00,091
不，你需要我的幫助，我和你一起去
No. You want my help, that I'm going with you.

542
00:34:00,157 --> 00:34:01,758
我也是 Me, too.

543
00:34:03,461 --> 00:34:06,696
固執、愚蠢
Stubborn, foolish.

544
00:34:06,763 --> 00:34:08,832
但是充滿了勇氣
But full of heart.

545
00:34:08,898 --> 00:34:11,268
好的 我們將一起旅行
Fine. We will travel together.

546
00:34:11,335 --> 00:34:13,070
所以我們要去哪裡？
So where are we going?

547
00:34:13,137 --> 00:34:17,607
洛基用瓦格護身符喚醒了芬利爾
Loki has awakened Fenrir with the Vargr amulet.

548
00:34:19,310 --> 00:34:22,079
但他衹有一半
But he only has one half.

549
00:34:22,146 --> 00:34:26,616
如果我們在他意識到他的錯誤之前找到另一半
If we find the other half before he realizes his mistake,

550
00:34:26,683 --> 00:34:28,586
我們有機會阻止芬利爾
we have a chance of stopping Fenrir

551
00:34:28,651 --> 00:34:30,287
來吞噬樹木
from devouring the tree.

552
00:34:30,354 --> 00:34:32,722
所以我們必須找到另一半的護身符
So we have to locate the other half of the amulet.

553
00:34:32,789 --> 00:34:34,325
的確 Indeed.

554
00:34:36,227 --> 00:34:39,597
薩吉亞斯 是的
Sagias. Yes.

555
00:34:39,662 --> 00:34:42,600
這是什麼？不是什麼，是誰
What is this? Not a what, who.

556
00:34:42,665 --> 00:34:44,368
尼古拉斯·薩吉亞斯博士
Doctor Nicholas Sagias.

557
00:34:44,435 --> 00:34:47,438
如果有人知道護身符的後半部分在哪裡
If anyone knows where to locate the second half of the amulet,

558
00:34:47,505 --> 00:34:48,606
他知道 he does.

559
